comments: Janine is fair, and always makes herself available for students. She volunteered her time to tutor our class on difficult material. She shows a true passion for her students, nursing and her patients. I learned more from her than any other instructor in all of school.

She is amazing, one of the best professors I\'ve ever had! She really cares about her students! She makes class interesting and memorable! I wish she was teaching more of the classes I still need to take! Thanks, Prof. McGrath :)

The best professor I have ever had! She has a vested interest in her students. She really wants everyone to do well, and to understand the topics. She is always willing to help. She has an amazing way of making you remember things. she is enthusiastic about nursing. She has an amazing amount of knowledge. Best prof in nursing program!

She teaches entirely through sarcasm, so attend class if you feel like being berated and abused. Her sarcasm gets annoying and gets in the way of a good lecture. Oh plus she treats you like 5 year olds. I\'ll never forget the day she came in and yelled at our entire class fo graduate students
